# Markdown Reference

## Badges
Below are some badges that should be shown at the top of your markdwon for any instrument. 
### Working Indicators
Use these badges to indicate a patch for a specific sampler is working.
* Ableton ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Working-blue?logo=abletonlive)
* Kontakt ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Working-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,);
})
* Sitala ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Working-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,);
})
* Decent Sampler ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Working-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,);
})
* Battery 4 ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Working-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,);
})
* Logic Sampler ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Working-blue?logo=apple)
### Not Working Indicators
Use these badges to indicate a patch for a specific sampler is either not working, does not exist, or is in progress.
* Ableton ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Invalid-red?logo=abletonlive)
* Kontakt ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Invalid-red?logo=data:image/png;base64,);
})
* Sitala ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Invalid-red?logo=data:image/png;base64,);
})
* Decent Sampler ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Invalid-red?logo=data:image/png;base64,);
})
* Battery 4 ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Invalid-red?logo=data:image/png;base64,);
})
* Logic Sampler ![Generic badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Invalid-red?logo=apple)
